---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout seoSlug="/refund-policy">
  <article class="legal">
    <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: 8 June 2026 · My Cosmic Message Pty Ltd t/a Asteris Commerce</p>
    <h2>14-day money-back guarantee</h2>
    <p>If Asteris Affiliates doesn't fit your store, email us within 14 days of purchase for a full refund. No questions, no friction.</p>
    <h2>How to request a refund</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Email <a href="mailto:support@asterisaffiliates.com">support@asterisaffiliates.com</a> with your order number or licence key.</li>
      <li>We process via Stripe within 3 business days.</li>
      <li>Refunds land back on your card in 5–10 business days (depends on your bank).</li>
    </ol>
    <h2>What's not refundable</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Renewals after 14 days from the renewal date.</li>
      <li>Migration assistance services already delivered.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Consumer rights</h2>
    <p>Australian Consumer Law applies. Nothing in this policy reduces your statutory rights under the ACL or your local consumer law.</p>
    <p><a href="/pricing">See pricing →</a> · <a href="/terms">Terms →</a></p>
  </article>
</Layout>
<style>
  .legal { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 96px 24px 64px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; }
  .legal h1 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .legal .meta { color: var(--c-muted); font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .legal h2 { font-size: 22px; margin: 24px 0 12px; }
  .legal ol, .legal ul { padding-left: 22px; }
  .legal li { padding: 6px 0; }
  .legal a { color: var(--c-mint); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
